Tap Into the Massive Market
The Gaming market is massive and continues to rise, with the global Market Revenue of $376 billion is generated by casual games. The marker-wide revenue is projected to reach $521.60 billion by 2027.
A Power of Web3 for Traditional Gamers
ScapesMania is a game built for the casual audience first, but with the help of Web3 we want to give players and crypto enthusiasts the ability to influence the development of the project.
What Is ScapesMania
ScapesMania is a gaming ecosystem that provides Web3 enthusiasts with opportunities to benefit and influence the development of projects made for a massive profitable casual game audience of Web2 players.
Get a unique opportunity to influence the development of an ecosystem for the mass audience and benefit from its success.
A Project Beyond P2E
The Play-To-Earn market is facing challenges and even the large titles see a drop in the user base and token prices. Traditional gamers are not interested in tokens and crypto entrepreneurs are not interested in games. We create a project that can satisfy both of those markets.

Revenue streams
The in-game economy is based on well-established Free-To-Play mechanics:
  • Buying Energy
    Allows players to start playing
  • Buying Boosters
    Allows Players to simplify certain in-game tasks
  • Timer Reduction
    Allows players to reduce the time needed for certain tasks
  • Decorative Items
    Players can buy unique objects and decorate their house or land with them
  • Premium Accounts
    Players can buy a monthly Premium subscription to avoid seeing ads and receive in-game bonuses
  • Ads
    Players can watch ads to receive in-game bonuses
  • Events
    Various events that boost player engagement and revenue

Game Description & Features

ScapesMania is a casual game for players that enjoy a captivating story, engaging mini-games and customization of their own house and garden, built in the Casual Art's setting.

Over the course of the game players will learn more about the town and its folks, will decorate their own house and land and participate in the local contest to become the best creator.

Customize Your Land
Players will have various tools to improve and decorate their homes and land.
Mini-Games
To earn resources for new decorations or story bits players will play engaging mini-games such as match-3.
Story
The town and its residents all have their unique stories and secrets to uncover.
Reputation
By completing personal errands for the townsfolk players will improve their relationship with them to uncover new story bits or additional gameplay features.
